                <a href="#" class="tag-badge" style="font-size: 0.9rem;">c#</a>
            </div>
            <p class="small text-muted mb-2" style="display: -webkit-box; -webkit-line-clamp: 3; -webkit-box-orient: vertical; overflow: hidden;">
                C# is a multi-paradigm programming language developed by Microsoft as part of .NET initiative.
            </p>
